organizations: Global Hydrology Resource Center, Marshall Space Flight Center, NASA
title: CAMEX-3 ER-2 NAVIGATION V1
summary: The CAMEX-3 ER-2 Navigation data files contain information recorded by on board navigation and data collection systems. In addition to typical navigation data (e.g. date, time, lat/lon and altitude) it contains outside meteorological parameters such as wind speed, wind direction, and temperature. These data are available in ASCII text file format and Graphics Interchange Format, where each file contains data recorded at one second intervals for each flight.
